title: Flowing Spring Pub
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. A traditional country pub that serves fresh, in-house-made food, including vegan and gluten-free. As of Feb 2015, the separate vegan menu has 4 starters, 9 main meals (including pizza with vegan cheese) and 3 desserts. Also has vegan margarine and soy milk.
